packages = c('rgdal', 'sf', 'spdep', 'tmap', 'tidyverse', 'maptools', 'raster', 'spatstat','prettydoc','spData','sp')
for (p in packages){
  if(!require(p, character.only = T)){
    install.packages(p)
  }
  library(p,character.only = T)
}

gym

mpsz_3414 <- st_set_crs(mpsz,3414)
## Warning: st_crs<- : replacing crs does not reproject data; use st_transform for
## that
gym_3414 <- st_set_crs(gym,3414)

mpsz_sp <- as_Spatial(mpsz_3414)
## Warning in showSRID(uprojargs, format = "PROJ", multiline = "NO"): Discarded datum Unknown based on WGS84 ellipsoid in CRS definition,
##  but +towgs84= values preserved
## Warning in showSRID(SRS_string, format = "PROJ", multiline = "NO"): Discarded
## datum SVY21 in CRS definition
gym_sp <- as_Spatial(gym_3414)
## Warning in showSRID(uprojargs, format = "PROJ", multiline = "NO"): Discarded datum Unknown based on WGS84 ellipsoid in CRS definition,
##  but +towgs84= values preserved

## Warning in showSRID(uprojargs, format = "PROJ", multiline = "NO"): Discarded datum SVY21 in CRS definition
gym_spdf <- SpatialPointsDataFrame(gym_sp,data.frame(id=1:159))


gym_res <- over(gym_spdf, mpsz_sp)

qtm()

mpsz_gym <- left_join(mpsz, gym_res, by = c("SUBZONE_N" = "SUBZONE_N"))

qtm(mpsz_gym, fill = "SUBZONE_NO.x")

tmap

tm_shape(mpsz_gym)+
  tm_polygons("SUBZONE_NO.x")

by region

tm_shape(mpsz_gym) +
  tm_fill("SUBZONE_NO.x",
          style = "quantile",
          palette = "Blues",
          thres.poly = 0) + 
  tm_facets(by="REGION_N.x", 
            free.coords=TRUE, 
            drop.shapes=TRUE) +
  tm_layout(legend.show = FALSE,
            title.position = c("center", "center"), 
            title.size = 20) +
  tm_borders(alpha = 0.5)
## Warning: The argument drop.shapes has been renamed to drop.units, and is
## therefore deprecated
